    },
    {
      "end": 115.26000213623047,
      "text": "It's all so easy to get carried away",
      "start": 110.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 116.91999816894531,
      "text": "And not remember this life",
      "start": 115.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 119.18000030517578,
      "text": "But don't teach me to die here",
      "start": 116.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 122.9800033569336,
      "text": "Don't teach me to not have that love inside of me",
      "start": 119.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 126.05999755859375,
      "text": "And watch out for your own perception of hate",
      "start": 122.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 128.8000030517578,
      "text": "All this negativity just dies",
      "start": 126.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 131.52000427246094,
      "text": "And makes you far away from yourself",
      "start": 129.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 134.8000030517578,
      "text": "And you can't hold down anything like your recourse",
      "start": 131.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 137.17999267578125,
      "text": "All your answers, everything",
      "start": 134.8000030517578
    },
    {
